{
 "name": "RPlog_SW1_Log_1999-12-06",
 "title": "SW1 Log: Frustrations in the Bay",
 "summary": "In a busy hangar bay, the towering Griffon Alliance officer Jonathan Steiner, trailed by fussing aides, and the stately Alderaanian diplomat Poguala Dawntreader contend with a day ruled by technical SNAFUs and balky ships. The bored pilot Bazil, fighting his own equipment troubles, wanders over to commiserate with Poguala, and the two share a quiet, sympathetic exchange about the strain everyone has been under since a recent attack and the weight of so many deaths. Meanwhile the officer Montgomery moves to cut off the brusque Steiner -- the Armiger -- for a private word. The scene blends shipboard frustration with moments of genuine human connection and grief.",
